Package: offs-relay
Version: 0.1.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.28), openssl (>= 3.0)
Maintainer: Prometheus-SCN <support@prometheus-scn.org>
Description: OFFS relay server
 A QUIC-based relay server for the Owner Free File System.
 This package installs the offs_relay binary to /usr/bin.
